data.description: Welcome to your dream home in North OKC! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.1-bathroom residence is a true gem. The spacious layout boasts not one, but two pantries, ensuring you have ample storage for all your kitchen needs. With two living rooms, there's plenty of space for both relaxation and entertainment. Don't worry about having too many clothes, your massive laundry room can help. Come on by today... won't last long!
